      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!), <strong>cornflour</strong>, 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span><strong> flour</strong> and <strong>egg<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>to a bowl and mix everything together</p><p>Crumble in the<strong> feta</strong>,<strong> </strong>season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and stir to combine – this is your<strong> fritter mixture</strong></p>",
